name: v1.7.8
body:
- Added Pinterest icon
- Updated Google Plus icon

name: v1.7.4
body: - Fixed doctype removing by the `iconizeHtml` method

name: v1.7.3
body:
- Fixed sprite multirendering (https://github.com/outpunk/grunt-evil-icons/issues/1)
- Fixed multiple icon classes (#57)

name: v1.7.1
body: - Crisp fix for non-retina screens, thanks to [@Ser-Gen](https://github.com/Ser-Gen)

name: v1.7.0
body: - Added brand colors for social icons

name: v1.6.0
body: - Added camera, Odnoklassniki, Soundcloud, Tumblr, Youtube, Vimeo and Skype icons

name: v1.5.0
body: - Added iconizeHtml method to the NPM package

name: v1.4.0
body: - Added credit card, like and trophy icons

name: v1.3.0
body:
- Added Linkedin and Instagram icons
- Fixed spinners animation performance (Thanks to [@legomushroom](https://github.com/legomushroom))

name: v1.2.0
body:
- Fixed cart icon
- Styles moved to assets/css.

- Sinatra support (Thanks to [@aderyabin](https://github.com/aderyabin))
- Spinners' animation improvement (Thanks to [@fliptheweb](https://github.com/fliptheweb))

- Smoothed icon shapes
- Switched from svg_optimizer to svgo
Lightweight SVG icons for your web project. Rails gem and npm package are available.
